S.FORM: Don Ackerman nalecuhan i New York City, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. 9 bulad 4 demiad, 1930 a mihca, Don Ackerman, miunduay. (mapatay i 2011 a mihca) namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
